query:
INSERT INTO BestProRecords (
                   filter_id,
                   player_id,
                   record_id,
                   points,
                   points_based_on_pro_leaderboard
                 )
                 VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, true)
                 ON DUPLICATE KEY
                 UPDATE record_id = VALUES(record_id),
                        points = VALUES(points)
